                                            </li>
                                            <li class="col-xs-6 col-sm-4 col-md-4" data-responsive="../img/lightbox-8.jpg" data-src="../img/lightbox-8.jpg" data-sub-html="<h4>Keyboard Navigation for desktop.</h4><p>Many desktop publishing packages and web page editors now use Lorem Ipsum as their default model text layout. </p>">
